The paper deals with distributed computing and network construction, which are topics typically covered in the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories. The paper also involves network topology and connectivity, which are relevant to the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-category.
